</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-author-date" -->
<div class="forum-post-template-post">
<p>Thanks, Jackx! this is exactly my view about healing...if you're going after it, in the sense of trying to fix something or hoping something will magically change, it doesn't happen. All of these "added things" (as Jesus called them) occur naturally when we "seek the kingdom first." The way I see it, it's fear that keeps us attached to the "I need this to happen" mindset.</p>
</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-post" -->
